entries.femaleVariant: Fuck, to fuck up a gig that bad... Man, really thought we'd get him outta there.
All that blood...! We're fucked. We were supposed to bring him in alive!
Well, we didn't. Not the first time, won't be the last. Might be a merc, but you're still human.
They'll zero us, just wait. Maybe in an hour, maybe in a week...
Hey, chill. Long as we're here, they can't touch us.
Hate to ruin your fuckin' airtight plan, there, but we can't just sit here forever!
And we won't. But first, need to calm down and think.
